Package: conversim
Title: Conversation Similarity Analysis Package
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Chao Liu", email = "chaoliu@cedarville.edu", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for analyzing and comparing conversations.
    This package provides functions to calculate various similarity measures
    between conversations, including topic, lexical, semantic, structural,
    stylistic, sentiment, participant, and timing similarities. It supports
    both pairwise conversation comparisons and analysis of multiple dyads.
License: GPL (>= 3)
